*cucumber-0.5.2 (22 Dec 2009)

  22 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump with new features to support cuke4duke and jruby.

*cucumber-0.5.1-r1 (18 Dec 2009)

  18 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  Install cucumber binary.

*cucumber-0.5.1 (18 Dec 2009)

  18 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Rails support has been split off to cucumber-rails.
  Converted to use ruby-fakegem.

  07 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -cucumber-0.3.100.ebuild,
  -cucumber-0.3.101.ebuild, -cucumber-0.3.103.ebuild,
  -cucumber-0.3.104.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  07 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add no-herd to metadata.

*cucumber-0.4.0 (13 Oct 2009)

  13 Oct 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*cucumber-0.3.104 (28 Sep 2009)

  28 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.3.104.ebuild:
  Version bump with support for steps in more programming languages.

*cucumber-0.3.103 (24 Sep 2009)

  24 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.3.103.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*cucumber-0.3.101 (19 Sep 2009)

  19 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.3.101.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  * New pdf formatter
  * Step Argument Transforms
  * Adding webrat steps for asserting content does or does not exist within 
    a particular element

